    ge: null, quarters: ["F", "W", "S", "SU"],
    desc: "How does one make decisions about those “big life” questions? From deciding “what the right thing to do to” is to how to have a career that enriches your life, how does one choose what to do? In this course, Cowell Alumni discuss how they made those “big life” decisions in the hopes that it can guide others. Course is designed to expand on the topics covered in COWL 140 , Designing Your Life.",
